tweet: Did you know that kids whose moms participated in WIC while they were pregnant score higher on cognitive development tests at age 2 than similar kids whose moms didn't participate in WIC? tweet: Don’t let a pre-Thanksgiving party squash your holiday meal. Here is a reminder that drinking & driving don't mix.
